{"id":97123,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2010/08/bbc中文：图辑：甘肃舟曲特大泥石流/","date":"2010-08-08T22:54:34Z","modified":"2010-08-12T04:04:50Z","title":"BBC中文：图辑：甘肃舟曲特大泥石流","content":"<div>\n<div>\n<div>\n<div>\n<ul>\n<li>\n<div>\n<div>\n<div><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://wscdn.bbc.co.uk/worldservice/assets/images/2010/08/08/100808135038_mudslide1_466x350_reuters.jpg\"><img src=\"http://www.bbc.co.uk/worldservice/ic/106x80/wscdn.bbc.co.uk/worldservice/assets/images/2010/08/08/100808135038_mudslide1_466x350_reuters.jpg\" alt=\"甘肃泥石流灾害（2010年8月8日）\" width=\"106\" height=\"80\" /></a></div>\n<div>8月8日，甘肃舟曲县发生特大泥石流灾害，造成严重人员伤亡。</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</li>\n<li>\n<div>\n<div>\n<div><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://wscdn.bbc.co.uk/worldservice/assets/images/2010/08/08/100808135426_mudslide2_280x350_ap.jpg\"><img src=\"http://www.bbc.co.uk/worldservice/ic/106x80/wscdn.bbc.co.uk/worldservice/assets/images/2010/08/08/100808135426_mudslide2_280x350_ap.jpg\" alt=\"甘肃泥石流灾害（2010年8月8日）\" width=\"106\" height=\"80\" /></a></div>\n<div>国务院总理温家宝亲临舟曲，指挥抢险救灾。</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</li>\n<li>\n<div>\n<div>\n<div><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://wscdn.bbc.co.uk/worldservice/assets/images/2010/08/08/100808140420_mudslide3_466x350_reuters.jpg\"><img src=\"http://www.bbc.co.uk/worldservice/ic/106x80/wscdn.bbc.co.uk/worldservice/assets/images/2010/08/08/100808140420_mudslide3_466x350_reuters.jpg\" alt=\"甘肃泥石流灾害（2010年8月8日）\" width=\"106\" height=\"80\" /></a></div>\n<div>中国媒体说，由于灾情发生在深夜，绝大多数人来不及逃生。</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</li>\n<li>\n<div>\n<div>\n<div><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://wscdn.bbc.co.uk/worldservice/assets/images/2010/08/08/100808140722_mudslide4_466x350_ap.jpg\"><img src=\"http://www.bbc.co.uk/worldservice/ic/106x80/wscdn.bbc.co.uk/worldservice/assets/images/2010/08/08/100808140722_mudslide4_466x350_ap.jpg\" alt=\"甘肃泥石流灾害（2010年8月8日）\" width=\"106\" height=\"80\" /></a></div>\n<div>洪水、泥石流冲毁了建筑物，煤气、水、电等基础设施被破坏。</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</li>\n<li>\n<div>\n<div>\n<div><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://wscdn.bbc.co.uk/worldservice/assets/images/2010/08/08/100808141234_mudslide5_466x350_reuters.jpg\"><img src=\"http://www.bbc.co.uk/worldservice/ic/106x80/wscdn.bbc.co.uk/worldservice/assets/images/2010/08/08/100808141234_mudslide5_466x350_reuters.jpg\" alt=\"甘肃泥石流灾害（2010年8月8日）\" width=\"106\" height=\"80\" /></a></div>\n<div>当局调遣大批部队，参加抢险。</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</li>\n<li>\n<div>\n<div>\n<div><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://wscdn.bbc.co.uk/worldservice/assets/images/2010/08/08/100808141450_mudslide6_466x350_reuters.jpg\"><img src=\"http://www.bbc.co.uk/worldservice/ic/106x80/wscdn.bbc.co.uk/worldservice/assets/images/2010/08/08/100808141450_mudslide6_466x350_reuters.jpg\" alt=\"甘肃泥石流灾害（2010年8月8日）\" width=\"106\" height=\"80\" /></a></div>\n<div>舟曲地方官员称，有些地方淤泥厚度超过1米，清理难度很大。</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</li>\n<li>\n<div>\n<div>\n<div><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://wscdn.bbc.co.uk/worldservice/assets/images/2010/08/08/100808141747_mudslide7_466x350_reuters.jpg\"><img src=\"http://www.bbc.co.uk/worldservice/ic/106x80/wscdn.bbc.co.uk/worldservice/assets/images/2010/08/08/100808141747_mudslide7_466x350_reuters.jpg\" alt=\"甘肃泥石流灾害（2010年8月8日）\" width=\"106\" height=\"80\" /></a></div>\n<div>中国今年遭受严重洪涝，据说，洪水已经造成1400人丧生。</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div></div>\n<p>请看原文：<br />\n<a title=\"图辑：甘肃舟曲特大泥石流\" href=\"http://feedproxy.google.com/~r/cnbbc/~3/0lWJV-EDRnU/100808_pic_gansu_mud.shtml\" target=\"_blank\">图辑：甘肃舟曲特大泥石流</a></p>\n","author":176,"categories":[20534],"tags":[9727,13464,13463,13732]}